CODE FOR MTRANS
      SUBROUTINE MTRANS(A)
C IN-PLACE TRANSPOSITION OF 3X3 MATRIX
C
      DIMENSION A(3,3)
      T = A(2,1)
      A(2,1) = A(1,2)
      A(1,2) = T
C
      T = A(2,3)
      A(2,3) = A(3,2)
      A(3,2) = T
C
      T = A(3,1)
      A(3,1) = A(1,3)
      A(1,3) = T
      END
