      SUBROUTINE XMULTR(A,B,C,N)
C--MULTIPLY THE 'N' ELEMENTS OF 'A' BY THE SCALAR 'B'
C  AND STORE THE RESULTS IN 'C'.
C
C  A  THE INPUT VECTOR.
